# Simple Calculator

This is a simple calculator application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It allows users to perform basic arithmetic operations such as addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.

## Features

- Addition
- Subtraction
- Multiplication
- Division

## Usage

1. Clone the repository to your local machine:

   ```
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/simple-calculator.git
   ```

2. Open `index.html` in your preferred web browser.

3. Enter the numbers you want to calculate and click on the corresponding operation button (+, -, *, /).

4. The result will be displayed in the output field.

